# Happy Path Testing for InternCodingChallenge

# TEST 1: VIEW ALL TICKETS
# Input Zendesk username
# Input Zendesk password
# Press enter
# All tickets in the Zendesk account will display as ticket ID and ticket subject, 25 at a time 

# TEST 2: VIEW A SINGLE TICKET
# Input Zendesk username
# Input Zendesk password
# Enter the following ticket ID: 1
# Press enter
# The ticket ID 1, ticket subject, and the ticket content will display 

# TEST 3: EXIT THE CLI TICKET VIEWER
# Input Zendesk username
# Input Zendesk password
# Enter the following character: x
# Press enter
# The message "Exiting. Goodbye!" will display and the user will return to the regular CLI prompt 
